No need to worry.

22
00:01:14.783 --> 00:01:18.620
I mean. I wasn't either when they
didn't know anything. but...

23
00:01:18.703 --> 00:01:20.622
Once the authorities reach out...

24
00:01:21.122 --> 00:01:25.710
...Eunice or Woosh could look into
the ongoing payments out of the club.

25
00:01:25.794 --> 00:01:28.463
This is such a headache!

26
00:01:31.466 --> 00:01:35.386
The whole reason I remarried
was because he was fun.

27
00:01:35.470 --> 00:01:39.265
Someone to eat with.
To travel with. That's all.

28
00:01:39.766 --> 00:01:43.686
Since we can't open
any shell companies at the moment.

29
00:01:43.770 --> 00:01:48.525
