138
00:08:25.129 --> 00:08:27.840
You and me both. Calvin. You and me both.

139
00:08:28.341 --> 00:08:31.594
Uh. so for any questions.
just go ahead and ask Woosh.

140
00:08:31.677 --> 00:08:35.473
who is running late again.
and he'll set you up.

141
00:08:35.556 --> 00:08:38.684
All right?
Let's go out there and be team MVP.

142
00:08:39.185 --> 00:08:43.523
They want to add
a body composition analyzer there. yeah?

143
00:08:43.606 --> 00:08:44.649
That's correct. yes.

144
00:08:44.732 --> 00:08:46.734
