209
00:11:58.426 --> 00:11:59.844
It's a bit complicated…

210
00:11:59.927 --> 00:12:04.181
If Penelope wants to chat more.
she can set a time for my office.

211
00:12:04.265 --> 00:12:07.643
Uh. Penelope's a little tight on money.
so just to ask it. what's your rate again?

212
00:12:09.353 --> 00:12:11.188
- Jimmy. it's such a fun game!
- No! No!

213
00:12:12.898 --> 00:12:14.567
What do you need. sweetie?

214
00:12:14.650 --> 00:12:16.736
I want her to go on the bounce house!

215
00:12:16.819 --> 00:12:18.654
Oh. I don't know about that. I'm--

216
00:12:23.492 --> 00:12:25.035
Please?

217
00:12:29.415 --> 00:12:32.501
Uh. sorry for the delay. fellas.
That eucalyptus mist should kick in now.

218
00:12:32.585 --> 00:12:33.836
And lunches are comped on me.

219
00:12:33.919 --> 00:12:36.297
Ah. appreciate you. Josh.

220
00:12:36.797 --> 00:12:38.466
- You're the man. Troy.
- Hey. Josh!

221
00:12:38.549 --> 00:12:41.385
I heard
Lindsay stopped by Gracie's birthday.

222
00:12:41.886 --> 00:12:43.220
- Oh. yeah?
- Yeah.

223
00:12:43.304 --> 00:12:45.181
Uh. sorry. who's… who's that speaking?

224
00:12:45.264 --> 00:12:46.390
It's Paul.

225
00:12:46.474 --> 00:12:48.726
Oh. yes. Paul. Of course. yeah.

226
00:12:48.809 --> 00:12:50.853
Oh. I didn't realize
Lindsay was stopping by.

227
00:12:50.936 --> 00:12:54.690
Yeah. Meredith told me your friend
