228
00:12:54.774 --> 00:12:57.693
Man. why didn't you come straight to me?
You know I got you.

229
00:12:57.777 --> 00:13:00.821
Oh. yeah! Sorry. yeah.
I should've done that.

230
00:13:00.905 --> 00:13:03.199
