should get a move on it though.

231
00:13:03.282 --> 00:13:05.367
Paul and Meredith book up fast.

232
00:13:05.451 --> 00:13:08.078
I got stuck with fucking Fred
on my divorce.

233
00:13:09.079 --> 00:13:10.790
The sooner you get going.
the better.

234
00:13:10.873 --> 00:13:14.251
