235
00:13:14.335 --> 00:13:17.880
It sounds like things could get
contentious with this husband's promotion.

236
00:13:17.963 --> 00:13:22.051
Oh wow. Cool. yeah. Sounds like Lindsay
really gave her the full download. huh?

237
00:13:22.134 --> 00:13:24.178
Have Penelope send that video too.

238
00:13:25.387 --> 00:13:26.222
Uh…

239
00:13:26.722 --> 00:13:28.474
Uh. sorry. who's… who's speaking now?

240
00:13:28.557 --> 00:13:30.684
-Bro. it's Billy.
-Oh. my bad.

241
00:13:30.768 --> 00:13:33.437
Uh. what exactly did Lindsay share
