242
00:13:33.521 --> 00:13:35.648
Not… not much. Let's chat after.

243
00:13:35.731 --> 00:13:37.358
We're ruining the steam sesh.

244
00:13:37.441 --> 00:13:38.859
Yeah. sure.

245
00:13:38.943 --> 00:13:41.028
-Whoa. Hey.
-Sorry about that… Yep.

246
00:13:41.111 --> 00:13:43.280
-Watch your back. bro.
-No. my bad. My bad. Okay.

247
00:13:43.364 --> 00:13:44.949
- Love you. Josh.
- Sorry. fellas.

248
