it was a temporary Band-Aid.

800
00:41:45.377 --> 00:41:46.712
Band-Aid for what?

801
00:41:48.589 --> 00:41:52.426
For the immense pain of knowing
that you picked the wrong person.

802
00:41:54.595 --> 00:41:55.471
Oh.

803
00:41:57.431 --> 00:41:58.349
Yeah.

804
00:42:00.017 --> 00:42:03.103
Yeah. in hindsight.
there were just so many signs.

805
00:42:03.187 --> 00:42:04.104
You just think.

806
00:42:04.605 --> 00:42:06.815
"How the fuck
did I not realize this sooner?"

807
00:42:06.899 --> 00:42:07.942
What kind of signs?

808
00:42:08.025 --> 00:42:09.818
Oh my God. so many. like.

809
00:42:10.402 --> 00:42:14.031
uh. the constant fighting that you saw.

810
00:42:14.114 --> 00:42:15.157
Um…

811
00:42:16.367 --> 00:42:18.452
The manipulating for attention.

812
00:42:18.536 --> 00:42:21.205
seeking affection
outside of the relationship.

813
00:42:21.872 --> 00:42:24.375
But that's just
normal ups and downs. right?

814
00:42:24.875 --> 00:42:27.294
I mean. don't people say that

815
00:42:28.462 --> 00:42:30.214
you shouldn't be looking
for the right person.

816
00:42:30.297 --> 00:42:32.132
but actually the right <i>wrong </i>person?

817
00:42:32.216 --> 00:42:36.428
Someone who's seen you at your worst
and you've seen them at theirs.

818
00:42:36.512 --> 00:42:38.180
but you still wanna stay?

819
00:42:39.723 --> 00:42:40.766
Yeah. maybe.

820
00:42:42.309 --> 00:42:43.811
Or maybe it's just…

821
00:42:44.562 --> 00:42:46.105
that's just something

822
00:42:46.814 --> 00:42:48.857
people tell themselves because

823
00:42:49.358 --> 00:42:52.152
it's too hard to admit that this thing.

824
00:42:52.236 --> 00:42:57.032
which finally gave your existence
some semblance of meaning.

825
00:42:58.284 --> 00:42:59.994
is just a sham.

826
00:43:03.330 --> 00:43:04.456
'Cause then what?

827
00:43:05.958 --> 00:43:07.835
You know. you're 40 years old

828
00:43:08.627 --> 00:43:10.879
without the faintest idea of who you are.

829
00:43:13.674 --> 00:43:15.092
Nobody wants that.

830
00:43:25.060 --> 00:43:27.271
You sure you want
to have a baby with Austin?

831
00:43:31.233 --> 00:43:32.651
Yeah. no. I'm sure.

832
00:43:36.614 --> 00:43:38.574
Well. let's sign up some more women. then.

833
00:43:43.329 --> 00:43:44.204
Cheers.

834
00:43:44.872 --> 00:43:46.624
You're my new best friend. man.

835
00:43:46.707 --> 00:43:47.875
I appreciate the talk. bro.

836
00:43:47.958 --> 00:43:49.752
Yeah. yeah.

837
00:43:49.835 --> 00:43:52.421
-Be kind to yourself. Okay?
-Yeah. Okay.

838
00:43:52.504 --> 00:43:54.923
We're gonna be drawn in
by other frequencies.

839
00:43:55.007 --> 00:43:56.091
Mm-hmm.

840
00:43:56.175 --> 00:43:58.218
-Other people. other women.
-Right.

841
00:43:58.302 --> 00:44:01.513
Just let it be. No judgments.

842
00:44:02.014 --> 00:44:03.724
No interpretations. Just…

843
00:44:04.516 --> 00:44:07.227
It's just harmony and dissonance.

844
00:44:07.311 --> 00:44:09.188
Harmony. dissonance.

845
00:44:09.271 --> 00:44:11.607
No. I know.
I just needed to talk it all out.

846
00:44:11.690 --> 00:44:13.984
-Yeah.
-I'm gonna focus on Ashley.

847
00:44:14.068 --> 00:44:15.736
-Yeah.
-Thanks.

848
00:44:21.784 --> 00:44:23.786
All right.

849
00:44:26.038 --> 00:44:27.081
Whoo!

850
00:44:32.920 --> 00:44:34.963
What the fuck?

851
00:44:38.258 --> 00:44:39.885
Dismantle…

852
00:44:41.345 --> 00:44:42.429
Fuck.

853
00:44:45.599 --> 00:44:47.267
Hey! You're back.

854
00:44:48.477 --> 00:44:51.563
Uh. sorry. I think you've mistaken me
for someone else.

855
00:44:51.647 --> 00:44:53.857
-Happens all the time.
-No. no. no. no.

856
00:44:53.941 --> 00:44:58.696
I distinctly remember your little car
driving by about a month ago.

857
00:44:59.905 --> 00:45:00.739
What?

858
00:45:00.823 --> 00:45:04.159
I thought to myself.
"What a nice pistachio color."

859
00:45:04.243 --> 00:45:08.914
I even told the Greek guy who lives here.
but he was so upset about his lost dog.

860
00:45:10.290 --> 00:45:11.792
Are you sure it was a Fiat?

861
00:45:11.875 --> 00:45:13.335
I'm pretty sure.

862
00:45:13.419 --> 00:45:16.296
I have the Ring footage on my phone.

863
00:45:19.049 --> 00:45:22.094
Um. may I see the footage. miss?

864
00:45:22.177 --> 00:45:24.096
Are you Polynesian?

865
00:45:26.432 --> 00:45:27.516
Sure.

866
00:45:27.599 --> 00:45:29.476
Beautiful night tonight.

867
00:45:31.311 --> 00:45:33.647
It's too dry. Bad for my skin.

868
00:45:33.731 --> 00:45:35.274
Your skin looks amazing though.

869
00:45:36.525 --> 00:45:39.445
What do you want to discuss?
I don't have time for this.

870
00:45:39.945 --> 00:45:40.863
Of course.

871
00:45:40.988 --> 00:45:43.949
I just wanted you to know that the
authorities in Seoul have contacted me.

872
00:45:44.742 --> 00:45:47.494
