874
00:45:52.875 --> 00:45:55.127
I know. I found it odd as well.

875
00:45:55.627 --> 00:45:57.629
I have to get ready for dinner.

876
00:45:57.713 --> 00:45:59.339
Will you help me with my necklace?

877
00:46:03.343 --> 00:46:05.387
For now. I said I know nothing.

878
00:46:05.471 --> 00:46:08.974
But if there's something
more specific I should say…

879
00:46:09.683 --> 00:46:11.518
There's nothing to say.

880
00:46:11.602 --> 00:46:15.647
That poor woman died of
a pre-existing condition.

881
00:46:16.648 --> 00:46:19.651
Once they find out you've been bribing
Trochos staff through the club...

882
00:46:20.903 --> 00:46:22.988
